comments: She knows what she is talking about. I enjoyed the class. She is an easy a if you actually put in effort. I like learning the material so for me the classes are easy. I took her twice and i got a\'s twice.

great professor very nice and helpful. the class itself was easy, the homework was easy and helpful to learn the material but her midterm and final were very hard and she dosent curve your grade on them thats the only con about this class but overall a great professor!

I know Natalie personally bc I\'ve done a CSI ride along with her and I think she would be a great teacher because she really cares if the person is actually learning.. I mean that\'s what u go to school for right?? She is an awesome teacher and I\'ve learned alot from her just doing a few ride alongs with her! If you want to REALLY learn take her classes and listen to her advice :)
